articles.author: Celia Ford
articles.title: A Groundbreaking Human Brain Cell Atlas Just Dropped - WIRED
articles.description: The comprehensive collection of 21 studies attempts to map all the brain’s cell types and offers hope of one day being able to trace brain diseases to their genetic roots.
articles.content: Today, an international team of researchers shared an extraordinarily detailed atlas of human brain cells, mapping its staggering diversity of neurons. The atlas was published as part of a massive pa… [+2649 chars]
